Author: remymartin1949
Text: I totally agree.  Have followed her from the beginning and noticed such a change in her physique as well as her content ( and not for the better).  She doesn't share much about her life (which I respect), but I'm sure there's some underlying issues (ie, her mother's health) that can affect  her eating.  I admire what she's doing and hope it'll contribute to her wellness.

Author: teapip99
Text: Idk if what she’s doing is healthy or not bc I’m Not a dietician or anything but I’m really proud of her for deciding not to starve herself for weeks and then just do a massive binge “cheat day”... I mean idk how well she’ll follow through with this but watching the video made me really happy for her
